translations.More info about the suspicious IP addres: Shubhali %s IP-manzil haqida ko'proq ma'lumot mavjud

translations.The suspicious login app is enabled on t: Ushbu misolda shubhali kirish ilovasi yoqilgan. U IP-manzillarni kuzatib boradi foydalanuvchilar muvaffaqiyatli tizimga kirishadi va shubhali IP-manzildan yangi login kelsa, ogohlantiruvchi Klassifikatorni yaratadilar.
translations.So far the app has captured {total} logi: Hozirgacha  {total} ilova qo'lga olindi, kirish (shu jumladan mijoz ulanishlari), ulardan{distinct} alohida (IP, uid) kataklar bor.
translations.No classifier model has been trained yet: Hali klassifikator modeli o'qitilmagan. Bu, ehtimol siz yaqinda dasturni yoqganingizni anglatadi. Modelni o'qitish yaxshi ma'lumotlarni talab qilganligi sababli, ilova kamida loginlarga qadar kutadi {days} kunda ochiladi.
translations.During evaluation, the latest model (tra: Baholash paytida eng so'nggi model (trained {time}) barcha shubhali loginlarning {recall}% of all suspicious logins (recall), ni qo'lga kiritishni ko'rsatdi, shubhali deb tasniflangan loginlarning {precision}% haqiqatan ham shubhali (aniqlik).
